-- ---- Table Comment ----
COMMENT ON TABLE main.de_output.de_output_appsflyer_silver_reports IS
'Silver-tier AppsFlyer mobile-attribution fact for the eToro OneApp Android / OneApp iOS apps. 133.9M rows, dates 2022-10-25 -> live (yesterday). Each row is one AppsFlyer raw-data-export record: Installs (paid attributed), OrganicInstalls (no paid touch / SKAdNetwork-restricted), or InAppEvents (post-install business events such as Open Trade, Registration_S2S, FTD_S2S, Verification Level - 1/2/3, Redeposit_S2S). Schema is exactly 1:1 with the AppsFlyer Raw Data Export API: 81 vendor-documented fields (attribution & touch, campaign & creative, cost, event & revenue, URL & referrer, location incl IP, device & network, device identifiers, app, multi-touch contributors 1/2/3) plus 5 eToro pipeline-added fields (DateID / Date / EtoroAppID / EtoroAppName / EtoroReport). Always filter EtoroReport (3 classes never sum cleanly) and EventSource IN (''SDK'',''S2S'') (~1M rows carry malformed JSON-fragment values). _S2S events are server-to-server postbacks and survive ATT-opt-out / ad-blockers / SDK init failures - prefer them over SDK siblings for revenue, FTD, registration counts. CID resolution: join AppsFlyerID -> bronze_marketperformance_tracking_customer.AppsflyerID.';

